{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Better With A Friend is a collection of hand drawn games specifically for the Steam Deck that you can only play with somebody else.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Better With A Friend is a homage to older games that I used to play back in the day during high school. Either on paper, some random flash game website, one of my first phones or a DOS PC that later became the Windows 95 computer. The time that it was virtually impossible to play against each other over the internet. Not counting those text based browser strategy games that my friends and I frequently visited during computer class. You basically had to be at the same place with all your friends to play games. For some games even sharing a keyboard or mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are 9 games in Better With A Friend at the moment!    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Also a quizmaster mode is added so you can use the questions with more friends in one of your own evening of trivia!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dots N Boxes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A classic from High School making sure you capture most of the boxes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943100/extras/Dots.png?t=1739008707\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Trivia</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you know better? Check your knowledge with Triva! Four categories are now included and more will be added over time! All questions are hand curated. There is now also a Quizmaster mode added that you can use if you need questions for your own night of games!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>TicTacToe</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The way to battle who needs to do the dishes: TicTacToe</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tennis</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An homage to older games needs to have Tennis included. One of the first games you could play together on the same screen at home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hangman</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you guess the word before the other one does? You only have so many attempts to do so.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sliding Puzzle</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you solve the puzzle together?!? A simple sliding puzzle to pass the time.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Memory</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Just a little game to pass the time. You make the rules how you want to play it with your friend! Are you going to time each other or take turns?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Checkers</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Just like you know it. Perfect game to play on the road together.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Guess the Flag</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you know more flags from around the world than your friend?\u00a0</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"You played the field","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2943100/94c9397877c6c932c455dc794d029f2e6ba57efa.jpg"},{"name":"Circle Wins","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2943100/03de1cbc16f8984f14e0b730ac3945ea5f4a00fd.jpg"},{"name":"Cross Wins","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2943100/4b